  "detailed_description": "Louis Devlin met and started dating a girl named Creasy. But something terrible happens and she is murdered.<br><br>Find out what happened next and solve the mystery of the scary mansion!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hide from monsters</strong></h2>Wandering through the dark corridors of various locations, hide from the entities that are chasing you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8947c49410c2614b6ec8403074ebaf77.poster.avif?t=1721155717\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8947c49410c2614b6ec8403074ebaf77.webm?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8947c49410c2614b6ec8403074ebaf77.mp4?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve puzzles</strong></h2>Explore buildings, collect items to open various locked doors, and discover what Alton Miles is hiding!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/25b2c0844192c9e19ab9322281adff84.poster.avif?t=1721155717\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/25b2c0844192c9e19ab9322281adff84.webm?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/25b2c0844192c9e19ab9322281adff84.mp4?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lock yourself in rooms</strong></h2>Use the keys to defend yourself from attacking evil monsters. It will take time for them to get through!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/0aaf84acad6085b001c8857225214aa5.poster.avif?t=1721155717\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/0aaf84acad6085b001c8857225214aa5.webm?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/0aaf84acad6085b001c8857225214aa5.mp4?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect the bloody eyes</strong></h2>Collect and use bloody eyes to get a look at the world from the monsters. Use them to find out their location and what they see!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8a6c50c55a16f8ffda0932ea7797fb1c.poster.avif?t=1721155717\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8a6c50c55a16f8ffda0932ea7797fb1c.webm?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979270/extras/8a6c50c55a16f8ffda0932ea7797fb1c.mp4?t=1721155717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
